{"type": "article", "id": 12506, "title": "“Ray-S” 扬声器", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-23T07:53:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145945wZ6J2dsXauGLUEYv.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t设计师 Charles 和 Ray Eames 夫妇被誉为 20 世纪最有影响力的设计师之一，它们在 1956 年推出的 Eames lounge chair &amp; ottoman，至今仍然是经典。最近，丹麦设计公司 Davone 以此为灵感来源，推出了 “Ray-S” 扬声器，外部箱体压制 16 层榉木制成，音色丰富，解析力强。设计师把古老的经典设计和当代科技结合在一起，喜欢那款经典躺椅的相信也会对这款扬声器感兴趣。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140238ADYBFOiz79XKvdar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140238MYH6B37fFGEQXtiv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00611247\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140239Yxl5EDo6UXCRh9zu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33251834\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140239r8dyWx2UGu9kiSoX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49266504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}